# WillyBeat Preset v2
version: 2
name:    Odd Time Prog Metal Fill
genres:  Metal, Prog Metal, Rock, Heavy, Aggressive, Dark, Progressive, Technical, Complex, Loud, Odd Time, Polyrhythmic, Djent, Math Metal, Virtuosic
type:    Big Fill
timesig: 4/4
